text.tspan: GDP per head vs share of services in employment, 1800 to 2015
The vertical axis shows historical estimates of the employment share in the service sector. The horizontal axis shows
GDP per head after adjusting for inflation and price differences across countries (figures are in 2011 international-$).
Source: OWID based on Herrendorf et al. (2014); GGDC-10 (2015); Maddison Project Database 2020 (Bolt and van Zanden, 2020)
